5000|$|His death {{cut short}} a {{collaboration}} with poet Antonio Porta, another Novissimo, {{on a project}} set {{to the music of}} Stratos' voice upsetting not only the avant-garde and experimental musicians who saw Stratos as one of their most important and representative members, but the entire show business community. The news spread in all directions, including media that was not so aware of alternative music. [...] At the time of his death, rumors circulated that his illness was caused by his secret and dangerous vocal practices. People <b>wanted</b> <b>to</b> <b>believe</b> <b>that</b> Demetrio Stratos had died due to daring too much and wandering outside the limits of human possibilities, as if he was a modern Icarus, punished for flying too close to the Sun.|$|E
